listen says fox it is music to run
over the hills to lick
dew from the leaves to nose along
the edges of the ponds… Mary Oliver 
🦊
have you ever seen a wild fox? this young female looked larger than life in the tall meadow grasses, but she was actually quite small. I think of her often and how beautiful, curious and brave she was.
